                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                        </head>
                        <p>On October 19 Messrs. Acheson, Snyder, and Foster met with M. Petsche to
                            discuss the French proposals contained in the memorandum of August 17.
                            For a summary of this discussion, see telegram <gloss target="#t_Todep1">Todep</gloss> 66 to London, October 19, <ref target="#pg_391">page
                                391</ref>.</p>
